Matata Traveller- Your Carefree Journey
By Aalifa designs (Sofia Bilal, Tuula Flynn, Gabriela Patrichi)

Tourist Guide Application


Overview
--------

Welcome to our Travel Guide – your gateway to an exciting world of cities, cultures, and flavors!
Discover cities anew through our curated blog posts, uncover hidden gems at renowned attractions,
and savor the essence of local cuisine. Stay informed with up-to-date currency exchange rates for each destination
and never be caught off guard by the weather, as we provide you with the latest forecasts.
Your journey begins here – explore the beauty of each city, one click at a time.

Goals / User Requirements:
--------------------------
From Users view:
1. The user can choose a city
2. The user can view detailed information about a city, including the name,
    country and a picture as well as specific threads, attractions
3. The user can enter a thread post
4. The user can update a thread post
5. The user can delete a thread post
6. The user can view all thread post for the city / reviews
    example categories for the threads: #food, #transport, #hotel, #restaurant, #excursion
7. The user can view threads posts for city, filtered by thread post category
8. The user can view the main attractions of the city.
9. The user can view details of each attraction (including pic)
10. The user will receive weather forecasts for their travel destination. TUULA
11. The user will be able to access a currency converter (calculate local currency rates) TUULA

Stretch goal:
-------------
The user can download a file containing a packing checklist and travel tips.
The user can request to add future cities in a form
The admin user can create, edit, update, delete articles for each destination.
If time permits, implement a language translator. Basic sentences.
// The user can fetch all blogs written by a specific user
The user can view the local cuisine of the city

Maybe create user credentials- log in - if implementing update and delete operations.
Either choose anonymous user.
Maybe use cities information API

Technical Specifications
--------------------------
Database: MySql (using ORM in java to interact with the database)
Backend: Java using Spring Data JPA framework
Frontend: VSCode Live Server plugin (not suitable for production)
N.B.a future development would be to look into getting the site hosted using AWS free cloud services.

Entities
---------
city_details
> city_id
> city_name
> city_country
// > weather third party done.
// > currency
(Optional) City_thread (city_details - thread_details - many to many )
> city_thread_id
> city_id
> thread_id
thread_details
> thread_id
> thread_content
> thread_category1
category1_details
> category_id
> category_name
(Optional) thread_category (because thread_details and category_details is a ManyToMany relationship)
> thread_category_id PK
> thread_id FK
> category_id FK
attraction_details
> attraction_id
> attraction_name
> attraction_description
> attraction_img
> attraction_open_time
> city_id (FK)


Third party data
—---------------------
weather_details
> weather_id
> weather_type
currency_details
> currency_id
> currency_name

Not using
---------
Cuisines
>cuisineId
>cuisineName
>cuisineUrl
>cuisineDish
Location
> locationId
> locationDescription
> locationLatitude
> locationLongitude
>locationAttraction FK




